---
title: Smokehouse Pulled Chicken Bowls with Buttery Jalapeño Corn, Pickled Shallot & Lime Crema
description: Do you love the flavor of saucy barbecue chicken but not the hours spent tending to the smoker? We’ve got you. Here, we’re sending ready-to-heat BBQ pulled chicken to cut down on precious time in the kitchen. It’s simmered with Southwest spices and lime juice, then piled into bowls with rice, jalapeño-flecked charred corn, pickled shallot, and lime crema. Everything’s ready in just 20 minutes for a meal that’ll have you totally BOWL-ed over.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smokehouse-pulled-chicken-bowls-e6772b98.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/smokehouse-pulled-chicken-bowls-5f5fa43ab7994b69f050a7e4-c340bc50.pdf
